extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: Celebrate the start of a new year with Secrets of Eternity, the new booster set packed with dozens of new cards befitting the occasion! Secrets of Eternity abounds with support cards for new tournament favorites, Burning Abyss, Shaddolls, and Stellarknights, as well as cards for recent introductions like Qliphorts, Performapals, and Superheavy Samurai. Devise wicked game strategies with a brand new diabolical theme. In addition to this new theme, Secrets of Eternity leaves virtually no Deck untouched, with support for even more Deck themes, including Gem-Knights, Dragunity, Morphtronics, Wind-Ups, Volcanics, Monarchs, and much more!
